, 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Drawings of male copulatory bulbs of Colombian Nopsma species. A, B. Nopsma florencia Sanchez-Ruiz, Brescovit &amp; Bonaldo. C, D. Nopsma macagual sp. nov. E, F. Nopsma leticia sp. nov. G, H. Nopsma paya sp. nov. A, C, E, G. Retrolateral view. B, D, F, H. Prolateral view. Scale bars: 0.7 mm. Abbreviations: e = embolus, mk = membranous keel, t = tegulum." figureDoi="10.3897/zse.97.69089.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/566385" pageId="0" pageNumber="383">6C, D</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
